a cold-pressed juice,

01:20.458 --> 01:22.375
so I will let you two
catch up

01:22.375 --> 01:23.834
and I will
be back shortly.

01:23.834 --> 01:26.959
Or not shortly
or whenever anyone
contacts me.

01:26.959 --> 01:29.500
- Okay, cool.
- Yeah, cool.

01:29.500 --> 01:31.542
Would anyone like
a juice or a tea?

01:31.542 --> 01:33.375
Actually, I could do
an apple juice
if you could--

01:33.375 --> 01:35.542
