01:47.750 --> 01:50.000
Oh, 'cause I woke up
in an alternate universe

01:50.000 --> 01:51.667
where up is down
and right is wrong?

01:51.667 --> 01:54.583
No, no,
it's completely fine.

01:54.583 --> 01:56.000
I'm sorry, this must
be fuckin' weird,

01:56.000 --> 01:57.333
but if I knew
you were coming home--

01:57.333 --> 01:59.583
What, you wouldn't
have had a girlfriend?

01:59.583 --> 02:01.875
No, I would've--
I would've warned you.

02:03.708 --> 02:05.500
It's just something
we're trying out.

02:05.500 --> 02:09.041
You were in love
with me a month ago.

02:09.041 --> 02:10.708
Yes, I know.

02:10.708 --> 02:14.000
