in a very unexpected way.

02:15.875 --> 02:17.583
I didn't break any rules.

02:17.583 --> 02:19.041
Nope, you didn't
break any rules,

02:19.041 --> 02:22.458
except maybe the rule
of common human decency,
Adam.

02:22.458 --> 02:24.959
Look, you made
the choice to leave.
You did that. I didn't do that.

02:24.959 --> 02:28.083
- Who the fuck is she?
- Her name is Mimi-Rose Howard.
She-- ( stammers )

02:28.083 --> 02:31.208
That's not a name.
That's just a woman's name
and a man's name

02:31.208 --> 02:32.708
