of the red hot lovers.

03:03.750 --> 03:08.417
Hannah, I want
you to understand,
this isn't about you.

03:08.417 --> 03:12.041
You know what, Adam?
I think I really understand
that part.

03:14.959 --> 03:17.083
Now if you'll excuse me,
I'm very tired from my journey

03:17.083 --> 03:19.750
and I'm gonna go take
a little rest in my room.

03:21.083 --> 03:22.917
Oh, okay.

03:24.083 --> 03:25.750
Um...

03:26.792 --> 03:30.166
( music playing )

03:30.166 --> 03:31.750
