could you have her
give me a call

03:49.708 --> 03:52.166
or just come to my place--
Hannah's place?

03:52.166 --> 03:55.959
Um, okay,
end of message.

03:59.708 --> 04:02.625
Maybe we should just leave
and let her stay here.

04:02.625 --> 04:04.417
No, no, you don't
know Hannah.

04:04.417 --> 04:06.333
She'll stay in there
until we have a new president.

04:06.333 --> 04:08.917
She's stubborn as fuck
and likes to be in bed a lot.

04:08.917 --> 04:10.917
Would it help
if I talk to her?

04:10.917 --> 04:13.166
