in a crisis.

04:13.166 --> 04:15.792
No fuckin' way.

04:15.792 --> 04:17.666
( knock on door )

04:21.625 --> 04:24.125
Oh, hi.
Marnie, right?

04:24.125 --> 04:27.333
No, not right,
and I don't know who you are
and I don't care to know.

04:27.333 --> 04:28.875
And that is all
I have to say about it.

04:28.875 --> 04:31.083
- Is she in here?
- Yes.

04:31.083 --> 04:34.333
- ( door closes )
- ( knocks softly )

04:34.333 --> 04:36.208
Banana?

04:36.208 --> 04:38.458
Hannah:
Mm-hmm?

04:40.417 --> 04:42.166
Oh, my God.

04:42.166 --> 04:44.250
- Hi.
- ( door closes )

04:44.250 --> 04:45.333
Hi, Shosh.

04:45.333 --> 04:48.291
