to a preverbal level.

10:06.083 --> 10:08.333
- So?
- So, call Marnie.

10:08.333 --> 10:10.458
I've already called
her stupid phone
like 10 times.

10:10.458 --> 10:12.667
- How do you find people like--
- ( door slams )

10:18.208 --> 10:19.834
( car horn honking )

10:19.834 --> 10:23.250
Hannah: This is a message
for her majesty,
Marnie Michaels.

10:23.250 --> 10:25.125
This is Hannah,
and this is the last message

10:25.125 --> 10:27.708
you'll be receiving from me
during our friendship,

10:27.708 --> 10:29.542
which is now over
because of the fact

10:29.542 --> 10:32.333
that you haven't
been here for me during
what could constitute

10:32.333 --> 10:34.375
the worst moment
of my entire life.

10:34.375 --> 10:37.667
And I'm stuck
in our old apartment
in my bedroom.

10:37.667 --> 10:39.875
There's a hole in the wall
to your bedroom.

10:39.875 --> 10:43.125
The place is seething
with intruders.

10:43.125 --> 10:45.291
And I have never
had to piss worse in my life,

10:45.291 --> 10:49.542
and probably no one else
in America has ever had
to piss worse than me.

10:49.542 --> 10:50.834
( clicks )

11:12.417 --> 11:14.917
( urinating )

11:17.208 --> 11:20.375
