13:38.542 --> 13:41.750
( music blaring )

13:56.750 --> 13:58.750
( door opens )

13:58.750 --> 14:01.041
Hey.

14:01.041 --> 14:02.959
Hi, um...

14:02.959 --> 14:04.708
is Adam here, or...?

14:04.708 --> 14:06.792
Ray:
No, it's just us.

14:06.792 --> 14:08.375
Okay.

14:10.542 --> 14:13.375
Oh. Okay.

14:13.375 --> 14:15.166
Thank you, Ray.

14:15.166 --> 14:17.750
So I guess you know
what's going on.

14:17.750 --> 14:21.208
I do.
I do and I'm sorry.

14:21.208 --> 14:24.250
I'm sorry
and I'm sickened.

14:24.250 --> 14:26.458
I'm not fine, Ray.

14:26.458 --> 14:28.667
I'm not fine at all.
I can't even pretend.

14:28.667 --> 14:30.875
This whole thing
feels like a puzzle

14:30.875 --> 14:34.041
with no possible solution,
like a Rubik's Cube.

14:34.041 --> 14:36.583
Those actually
do have solutions.

14:36.583 --> 14:38.792
