that open-ended.

14:44.458 --> 14:47.083
People can be
so fucked up,
Hannah, you know?

14:47.083 --> 14:49.125
They lie,
they obfuscate,

14:49.125 --> 14:50.417
and then if that
wasn't enough,

14:50.417 --> 14:52.125
on top of it all,
they think they can
get away with it

14:52.125 --> 14:53.250
because
everyone else does.

14:53.250 --> 14:55.708
- Yeah.
- Do you understand
how malignant

14:55.708 --> 14:58.417
and ethically bankrupt
that logic is?

14:58.417 --> 14:59.834
You deserve justice.

14:59.834 --> 15:03.041
I deserve justice,
and together, by God,
we will have justice.

15:03.041 --> 15:05.125
Come hell or high water,
we will have our justice.

15:05.125 --> 15:07.000
Can you flip
the bacon, please?

15:07.000 --> 15:08.750
Are you, um, okay, Ray?

15:08.750 --> 15:11.083
